      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "URANA SPACE (7) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts two wins and three placings. In the money last time at Murray Bridge (39.69) in a Special conditions race, finishing a 1.75 lengths second. Rates on top and should go close. LOOSE MOOSE (1) placed two runs ago then again in the money last time when third (43.98) at Angle Park in a Grade 5/6. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. LIL REX (5) scored over 530m at Angle Park last time when leading throughout to claim a Special conditions race (30.41) latest. First time stretching out to a staying journey. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Capable of going well again. REALITY IS (3) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
